      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOLLER NUFF (8) missed narrowly fresh before getting the job done at his last start over 1200m at this track. We'll get a guide on his form in the opening event of the day, with this son of Justify stepping up to the mile today. CJP sticks third-up and he can bring up back-to-back wins. STYLISH LORD (1) is racing well without winning, being in the finish in stronger races than this recently. He comes into this on the fresh side and gets some help with ZJP's claim. Won't have to work too hard from the good draw today and can return to the winners list. MACCIATEAU (7) is one who is going better than his form suggests. He stuck on well behind a smart one last time out and now gets a chance to sit closer from a good draw today. Like the way he's ticking along and now he gets his chance. MORE THAN ENUFF (6) is fitter now and can improve on the fresh effort. MANHATTAN STRIP (9) is right in this on his best form.",
